<HEADLINE>
<P>
NO-HITTER THROWN AGAINST DODGERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Atlanta pitcher Kent Mercker threw the first no-hitter of the season as the 
Braves beat the Dodgers, 6-0, Friday night at Dodger Stadium. C1 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Infobox 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
