Kent Mercker Atlanta 6-0 July 28, 1991 Dennis Martinez* Montreal 2-0 Sept. 16, 
1988 Tom Browning* at Cincinnati 1-0 Sept. 26, 1982 Nolan Ryan at Houston 5-0 
Aug. 9, 1976 John Candelaria at Pittsburgh 2-0 * perfect game 
</P>
