 Los Alamitos 3, Western 0 -- Tim Tamas and Pete Young each had seven kills and 
Tim Cockriel added 30 assists to lead Los Alamitos, 15-10, 15-12, 16-14. Los 
Alamitos is 2-3, 2-0. 
</P>
