</P>
<P>
 Corona del Mar 3, Saddleback 0 -- Brian Coleman had 10 kills, Clay Burton had 
eight, Andy Peykoff had 30 assists and Brad Callahan had six blocks and four 
kills to lead Corona del Mar past Saddleback, 15-2, 15-5, 15-10. Corona del Mar 
is 7-1, 5-1. 
</P>
