<HEADLINE>
<P>
SANTA MARGARITA'S BROWN GOING TO UCLA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Tiffany Brown, a two-time All-Sea View League girls' soccer player and The 
1994 Times all-county selection as a defender for Santa Margarita High, has 
committed to attend UCLA, she said Friday. 
</P>
<P>
 Brown was a four-year starter for the the Eagles. She becomes the first to 
receive a scholarship in girls' soccer at Santa Margarita since the program 
started in 1987. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
