(2:07.52) and Craig McMillan won the 1,000 freestyle (10:12.28) to help lead 
host Orange Coast. Andrade and McMillan teamed with Edward Sick and Matt 
Panighetti to win the 400 freestyle relay for the Pirates. 
</P>
<P>
 In the South Coast Conference: 
</P>
<P>
 Long Beach 54, Golden West 49; Golden West 84, Pasadena 10 -- Golden West lost 
eight unanswered points to Long Beach because of its lack of divers, and lost 
for the first time this season. Matt Braun and Chris Koerner were 
multiple-event winners for Golden West (4-1). Braun won the 1,000 freestyle 
(10:18.80) and 500 freestyle (4:59.85). Koerner won the 50 freestyle (22.15) 
and teamed with Braun for the winning 400 medley relay team (3:23.29). 
