</P>
<P>
 Golden West 107, Long Beach 23; Golden West 115, Pasadena 5 -- Golden West won 
all 14 swimming events to remain undefeated at 5-0. Kate Kilgallen and Belinda 
Kernkamp were multiple-event winners for Golden West. Kilgallen won the 100 
backstroke (1:09.88) and 50 backstroke (32.60). Kernkamp won the 50 freestyle 
(26.98), 500 freestyle (5:54.48) and anchored the winning 200 medley relay 
(2:04.90) and 200 freestyle relay (1:50.06). 
