 Shackelford Golf, owned by former college basketball star Lynn Shackelford, 
will spruce up the grounds with new landscaping, replace the course's sprinkler 
system and install a net at the end of the greens to keep balls from flying 
into neighboring property. 
</P>
<P>
 Shackelford said he will also renovate the pro shop, a former gas station that 
needs roof repairs and a paint job. 
</P>
<P>
 "The district has run the course all these years, nd it's been a low-cost 
facility for youth, seniors and new golfers,"Gladden said. "Now we're giving it 
a chance to be a nicer place to 1735355494SARA CATANIA. 
