<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRIEFLY: LABOR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Staff and Wire Reports 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Teamsters to Meet With 18 Small Trucking Firms: The union will meet today with 
officials from the companies that want to resume operations after being shut 
down by a nationwide strike.The firms would operate under an interim agreement 
until the strike is settled and a final contract is reached. No negotiations, 
however, are scheduled with the four largest trucking firms hit by the 
