athletes to tonight's Arcadia Invitational track and field meet at Arcadia High 
(C14). . . . Who knows? Today, Arcadia. Tomorrow, Atlanta and the 1996 
Olympics. It's happened before. Olympic medalists Gail Devers, Mike Powell, 
Quincy Watts and Valerie Brisco all competed at the Arcadia meet, which began 
in 1968 without much fanfare. Michael Arkush 
