 Corporate officers -- Irwin Bransky, founder and president of Kenfil Inc., the 
Van Nuys software distributor that has agreed to be acquired by AmeriQuest 
Technologies Inc. of Irvine, will report directly to AmeriQuest's president as 
head of the merged companies' software division. A story in Wednesday's Valley 
